metadata.name: Stamen
metadata.description:
The Bollz is the first limited edition drop of 100 utility-enabled NFTs by Pillz Inc. Each Bollz is your entry ticket into the Pillz ecosystem. It offers the holder a unique opportunity to claim it and get a wearable phygital device for NFT-collectibles with set of fittings and original 1 of 1 interactive NFT pet from the Bollz family.

Regarding the traits of Bollz, there are REDEEMED “YES” & “NO” versions - in the “YES” versions the physical has already been redeemed so DO NOT purchase if you intend to get the physical. The “YES” version is just a digital collectible.

To get their Pillz - Bollz NFT holders must claim it before December, 31st 2023. 

Token burnt at Sat Feb 04 2023 09:46:02 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)
